      +==========+             +==========+ S:OPEN                      |
 +----| HDR-RCVD |             | HDR-SENT |------+                      |
 |    +==========+             +==========+      |      R:HDR[!=S:HDR]  |
 |   S:HDR |                      | R:HDR        |    +-----------------+
 |         +--------+      +------+              |    |                 |
 |                 \\|/    \\|/                   \\|/   |                 |
 |                +==========+               +-----------+ S:CLOSE      |
 |                | HDR-EXCH |               | OPEN-PIPE |----+         |
 |                +==========+               +-----------+    |         |
 |           R:OPEN |      | S:OPEN              | R:HDR      |         |
 |         +--------+      +------+      +-------+            |         |
 |        \\|/                    \\|/    \\|/                  \\|/        |
 |   +===========+             +===========+ S:CLOSE       +---------+  |
 |   | OPEN-RCVD |             | OPEN-SENT |-----+         | OC-PIPE |--+
 |   +===========+             +===========+     |         +---------+  |
 |  S:OPEN |                      | R:OPEN      \\|/           | R:HDR   |
 |         |       +========+     |          +------------+   |         |
 |         +----- >| OPENED |< ---+          | CLOSE-PIPE |< -+         |
 |                 +========+                +------------+             |
 |           R:CLOSE |    | S:CLOSE              | R:OPEN               |
 |         +---------+    +-------+              |                      |
 |        \\|/                    \\|/             |                      |
 |   +============+          +=============+     |                      |
 |   | CLOSE-RCVD |          | CLOSE-SENT* |< ---+                      |
 |   +============+          +=============+                            |
 | S:CLOSE |                      | R:CLOSE                             |
 |         |         +=====+      |                                     |
 |         +------- >| END |< ----+                                     |
 |                   +=====+                                            |
 |                     /|\                                              |
